---
layout: base
title: The Freethinker's Bookshelf
description: A curated, annotated reading list for the intellectually curious — books that shaped the freethinking tradition and books that should.
permalink: /bookshelf/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-12); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">

  <header class="project-section-header">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol class="breadcrumbs__list">
        <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a class="breadcrumbs__link" href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a class="breadcrumbs__link" href="/projects/">Projects</a></li>
        <li class="breadcrumbs__item breadcrumbs__item--current" aria-current="page">Bookshelf</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>
    <span class="section-badge section-badge--bookshelf">Bookshelf</span>
    <h1>The Freethinker's Bookshelf</h1>
    <p class="project-section-lede">Not a recommended reading list, but a considered one. Every book here earns its place by doing something specific: advancing an argument, documenting a tradition, or forcing more careful thought. Each annotation tells you what the book does and what it doesn't — including where it goes wrong.</p>
    <p style="font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-top: var(--space-4);">
      Think a book belongs here? <a href="/bookshelf/submit/" style="color: var(--color-link); font-weight: 600;">Recommend it</a>
    </p>
    <div style="margin-top:var(--space-4);display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/bookshelf/timeline/" class="btn">View as Timeline</a>
      <a href="/bookshelf/showcase/" class="btn">Showcase</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="bookshelf-grid">
    {% for book in collections.bookshelf %}
    <article class="book-card">
      <header>
        {% if book.data.category %}
        <p class="book-card__category">{{ book.data.category }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <h3 class="book-card__title"><a href="{{ book.url }}">{{ book.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p class="book-card__author">{{ book.data.bookAuthor }}{% if book.data.year %} · {{ book.data.year }}{% endif %}</p>
      </header>
      <p class="book-card__description">{{ book.data.description }}</p>
      <a href="{{ book.url }}" class="book-card__link">Explore this book →</a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
